annotationA: Protein brunelleschi; Cooperates with Rab11 and fwd/PI4K to mediate the flow of membrane through the Golgi, which is required to support cleavage furrow ingression, therefore promoting cytokinesis in male meiotic cells
annotationB: Trafficking protein particle complex subunit; May play a role in vesicular transport from endoplasmic reticulum to Golgi
